Invocation Name: radio des elus
des: Welcome to Radio des Elus of Brockton, as a gospel radio station we been serving the community of Brockton since December 2015 by encouraging our listeners with the hope of God trough some christian music and other spiritual meditation programs. We are a listener-supported radio network—our mission is to create compelling media that inspires and encourages you to have a meaningful relationship with God."The skill content is in English, French and Haitian creole language."
